--[[

    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║   User Interface Library  —  Stellar  v3.0              ║
    ║   Original: Friskl  |  v2.0 → v3.0 Major Overhaul        ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    CHANGELOG (v3.0 — Major Overhaul):

    ── ARCHITECTURE  ─────────────────────────────────────────
    • FIX: Per-window Theme/Setup (no more module-level mutation
          → opening 2 windows with different themes no longer
          clobbers each other).
    • FIX: ShiftColor now uses per-window ThemeMode.
    • FIX: Animations:Open captures Size from each call site
          (no module-level Setup.Size dependency).
    • NEW: Centralised InputHub — a single global InputChanged
          / InputEnded subscription that fans out to subscribers.
          Replaces 3× listener per ColorPicker, etc.
          (5 pickers used to fire 15 listeners/frame → now 1.)

    ── BUG FIXES ─────────────────────────────────────────────
    • MakeDraggable: per-mousedown `Input.Changed` no longer
      tracked by the WinMaid (leaked one connection per click).
      Now uses a single InputEnded listener.
    • Keybind: DetectConn now ONLY removed via WinMaid — no
      double-disconnect on success.
    • Slider: StopSliding is idempotent and connections are
      cleared even if Heartbeat fires after Active=false.
    • Dropdown / MultiDropdown: per-button Connect() calls now
      tracked by an ephemeral Maid for that dropdown panel,
      destroyed alongside the panel.
    • Cfg.Tab defensiveness: every Add* validates Cfg.Tab and
      warns instead of throwing a cryptic nil error.

    ── MOBILE  ───────────────────────────────────────────────
    • Slider: tap-anywhere on the track jumps to that value
      (no need to hit the tiny Fire dot).
    • Larger touch zones for Toggle, Button, Dropdown, Keybind,
      ColorPicker on IsMobile (heights bumped 12–24 px).
    • ColorPicker SV canvas larger on mobile (130 → 160 px).
    • Floating Action Button (FAB) — shows in bottom-right when
      window is hidden on mobile; one tap to re-open. Drag to
      reposition. Long-press to fully destroy.
    • Haptic feedback on Toggle, Button, Slider commit (via
      HapticService).
    • Long-press → Tooltip (mobile equivalent of mouse hover).
    • Notifications stack from top on portrait phones (avoids
      thumb / system-UI bottom area).

    ── NEW COMPONENTS  ───────────────────────────────────────
    • AddTooltip(component, text)        — hover (PC) / long-press (mobile)
    • AddConfirmDialog(title, body, fn)  — modal yes/no
    • AddSearchableDropdown(...)         — dropdown + filter box
    • Section collapse/expand (auto if AddSection called with Collapsible=true)
    • AddTabBadge(tabName, text)         — small pill on tab button

    ── COMPONENT API UNIFICATION  ────────────────────────────
    Every Add* now returns a control table with at least:
        :Set(value)         :Get()
        :OnChanged(fn)      :Destroy()
        :SetVisible(bool)
        :SetTitle(str)      :SetDescription(str)
    (Where a method does not apply, it is a safe no-op.)

    ── CONFIG SAVE / LOAD  ───────────────────────────────────
    • Options:GetConfig()   — returns a table of {flag = value}
    • Options:LoadConfig(t) — applies values back to components
    • Components are auto-registered if Cfg.Flag is supplied.

    ── ANIMATIONS  ───────────────────────────────────────────
    • Spring tween helper (Quint/InOut, softer feel).
    • Component-add slide-in animation.
    • Tab switch cross-fade (no more flash of empty content).

    ── PERFORMANCE  ──────────────────────────────────────────
    • Theme engine: per-window descendant cache, rebuilt only
      when components are added (was full O(n) sweep on every
      theme change × every window).
    • InputHub batching: a single InputChanged drives all
      drag-style components.

    ── WINDOW API  ───────────────────────────────────────────
    Options:Destroy()         — full teardown (every connection)
    Options:SetVisible(bool)  — animated show/hide
    Options:OnThemeChanged(fn)
    Options:GetConfig()  / Options:LoadConfig(t)
    Options:SetTab(name)
    Options:Notify(cfg)
    Options:Confirm(cfg)      — promise-like; returns task-spawned
    Options:Tooltip(comp, text)

]]


